@node "Vect-X" "Another midi.library program"
Vect-X is a MIDI vector synthesis program which provides cross-modulation of
volume, pitch, panning, reverb, filter etc on upto four MIDI channels. It can
be used to create very atmospheric pad sounds... and more!
@endnode

